## Live verification

Same scenario as PR #185: haiku-4-5 main + opus-4-7 advisor via
litellm.singula.ai in headless mode. README.md created cleanly,
exit 0, advisor invocation worked through the new renderer + helper
modules.

## What's NOT in this PR (deferred)

Final `agent_loop.py` deletion (Stage 4 proper). Requires porting
~50 tests across 6 files from `run_agent_loop` → `run_query_as_agent_loop`,
which is meaningful work and deserves its own PR after this burns
in. The current shim is small enough (210 loc, no production
consumers) that keeping it for one cycle is fine.

